<HL>
   Copperweld to Plan Meeting
</HL>
<DATE>
04/02/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   COS
</CO>
<LP>
   PITTSBURGH -- Copperweld Corp. said it delayed preparation
of its annual report and proxy statement until the company
selects a date for a special shareholders meeting to vote on
a merger offer.
   The company previously announced that a special committee
of directors is evaluating a merger proposal from Imetal
S.A., a French metals company that is Copperweld's largest
shareholder.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Copperweld, a producer of wire, cable, rods and tubing,
said it expects to mail its proxy statement to shareholders
by May 15.
</TEXT>
